 <div class="table-responsive"> 
  <table class="wiki_table"> 
   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Furlcalling Finger Remedy</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img title="Furlcalling Finger Remedy" src="/file/Elden-Ring/furlcalling_finger_remedy_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="furlcalling finger remedy elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Type</td> 
     <td>Consumable</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <img src="/file/Elden-Ring/status_effect_113_elden_ring_wiki_guide_44px.png" alt="status effect 113 elden ring wiki guide 44px" width="21" height="21">&nbsp;Reveals co-op and hostile summoning signs 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Furlcalling Finger Remedy</strong>&nbsp;is a <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Multiplayer Items" href="/Multiplayer+Items">Multiplayer Item</a>&nbsp;and <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Consumables" href="/Consumables">Consumable</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Multiplayer Items</strong> allow players to interact with each other in various ways, including leaving messages for other players to read, co-operative gameplay and competitive gameplay like PVP.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>Item for online play.<br> (Can also be used from the Multiplayer menu.)<br> Craftable item.<br></em></p> 
 <p><em>Reveals cooperative and competitive multiplayer signs.<br> Co-op summoning signs will be shown in gold, while hostile summoning signs will be shown in red.<br></em></p> 
 <p><em>Multiplayer begins when you summon a player from another world through their sign.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Furlcalling Finger Remedy Location in&nbsp;Elden Ring</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Furlcalling Finger Remedy</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Dropped by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Bloody Finger Nerijus" href="/Bloody+Finger+Nerijus" target="">Bloody Finger Nerijus</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=6901&amp;lat=-186.710937&amp;lng=110.410842&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=6901&amp;lat=-186.710937&amp;lng=110.410842&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</li> 
 <li>Dropped by Hosts of Fingers when invading.</li> 
 <li>Dropped by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Recusant Henricus" href="/Recusant+Henricus" target="">Recusant Henricus</a>&nbsp;when invading. North-East of <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stormhill Shack" href="/Stormhill+Shack" target="">Stormhill Shack</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=533&amp;lat=-173.46875&amp;lng=99.675821&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=533&amp;lat=-173.46875&amp;lng=99.675821&amp;zoom=8">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</li> 
 <li>Dropped by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Anastasia, Tarnished-Eater" href="/Anastasia,+Tarnished-Eater" target="">Anastasia, Tarnished-Eater</a> when invading. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=981&amp;lat=-170.65625&amp;lng=124.164723&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=981&amp;lat=-170.65625&amp;lng=124.164723&amp;zoom=8">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</li> 
 <li>Dropped in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Highroad Cave" href="/Highroad+Cave" target="">Highroad Cave</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring interactive map?id=3881&amp;lat=-173.078125&amp;lng=108.39113&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/interactive+map?id=3881&amp;lat=-173.078125&amp;lng=108.39113&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</li> 
 <li>Players can buy&nbsp;it from <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Merchant Kalé" href="/Merchant+Kalé" target="">Merchant Kalé</a>, for 1000 Runes.&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=4&amp;lat=-191.1875&amp;lng=100.041878&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=4&amp;lat=-191.1875&amp;lng=100.041878&amp;zoom=8">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</li> 
 <li>Can be purchased from&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Twin Maiden Husks" href="/Twin+Maiden+Husks" target="">Twin Maiden Husks</a>&nbsp;at the&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Roundtable Hold" href="/Roundtable+Hold" target="">Roundtable Hold</a>&nbsp;after giving them&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Kale's Bell Bearing" href="/Kale's+Bell+Bearing" target="">Kale's Bell Bearing</a></li> 
 <li>Can be found in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Castle Morne" href="/Castle+Morne" target="">Castle Morne</a>. From the main courtyard, hug the right wall past the burning corpses and <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Misbegotten" href="/Misbegotten">Misbegotten</a> to reach the northern building and follow the linear path to reach the top level. The item is found on a corpse next to the gallows. [<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=757&amp;lat=-225.882812&amp;lng=107.488511&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=757&amp;lat=-225.882812&amp;lng=107.488511&amp;zoom=8">Map Linik</a>] <a class="wiki_link" title="Video Location" href="https://youtu.be/X-OGSFqjTO0?t=610">Video Location</a></li> 
 <li>One can be looted off a corpse at <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stormveil Castle" href="/Stormveil+Castle" target="">Stormveil Castle</a>. When you reach the heavily guarded courtyard, head to the spot where the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Omen" href="/Omen" target="">Omen</a>&nbsp;is which is at the northwest side. You'll find the corpse lying on the ground of the stairs.&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=6903&amp;lat=-176.90625&amp;lng=86.34931&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=6903&amp;lat=-176.90625&amp;lng=86.34931&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Video Location" href="https://youtu.be/7zS9MfxqlCs?t=575">Video Location</a></li> 
 <li>Sold by&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patches" href="/Patches" target="">Patches</a>&nbsp;at&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Murkwater Cave" href="/Murkwater+Cave" target="">Murkwater Cave</a>&nbsp;after he sets up shop.&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Video Location" href="https://youtu.be/7zS9MfxqlCs?t=255">Video Location</a></li> 
 <li>Can be purchased from&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Twin Maiden Husks" href="/Twin+Maiden+Husks" target="">Twin Maiden Husks</a>&nbsp;at the&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Roundtable Hold" href="/Roundtable+Hold" target="">Roundtable Hold</a>&nbsp;after giving them&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patches' Bell Bearing" href="/Patches'+Bell+Bearing">Patches' Bell Bearing</a></li> 
 <li>One can be found on a corpse sitting in the water near the Siofra River Well Depths <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sites of Grace" href="/Sites+of+Grace">Site of Grace</a> in the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Siofra River" href="/Siofra+River">Siofra River</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=1186&amp;lat=-187.701562&amp;lng=123.208553&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB" href="/Interactive+Map?id=1186&amp;lat=-187.701562&amp;lng=123.208553&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</li> 
 <li>One can be found&nbsp;on the ground level of the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Siofra River" href="/Siofra+River">Siofra River</a> right next to the wall surrounded by a group of <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Land Octopus" href="/Land+Octopus">Land Octopuses</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=1161&amp;lat=-180.171875&amp;lng=133.571215&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB" href="/Interactive+Map?id=1161&amp;lat=-180.171875&amp;lng=133.571215&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a></li> 
 <li>Can be found on one of the corpses lying on the stairs leading up to a ruin in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ainsel River" href="/Ainsel+River">Ainsel River</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=1365&amp;lat=-129.117187&amp;lng=68.957409&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB" href="/Interactive+Map?id=1365&amp;lat=-129.117187&amp;lng=68.957409&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a></li> 
 <li>Found on a corpse dangling off of the edge of the ruins in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Nokron, Eternal City" href="/Nokron,+Eternal+City">Nokron, Eternal City</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=1538&amp;lat=-187.09375&amp;lng=120.674698&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB" href="/Interactive+Map?id=1538&amp;lat=-187.09375&amp;lng=120.674698&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapB">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a></li> 
 <li>Dropped by <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Festering Fingerprint Vyke" href="/Festering+Fingerprint+Vyke" target="">Festering Fingerprint Vyke</a>&nbsp;when invading. [<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=1858&amp;lat=-115.929687&amp;lng=71.531852&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=1858&amp;lat=-115.929687&amp;lng=71.531852&amp;zoom=8">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>]</li> 
 <li>Looted off a corpse hanging on the fence of the second-floor balcony. The nearest site of grace is the Schoolhouse Classroom in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Raya Lucaria Academy" href="/Raya+Lucaria+Academy" target="">Raya Lucaria Academy</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=2214&amp;lat=-139.179687&amp;lng=56.206009&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=2214&amp;lat=-139.179687&amp;lng=56.206009&amp;zoom=8">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a></li> 
 <li>Looted off a corpse in the middle part of the Iron Ball trap stairs in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Raya Lucaria Academy" href="/Raya+Lucaria+Academy" target="">Raya Lucaria Academy</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=2286&amp;lat=-135.65625&amp;lng=59.197738&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+Map?id=2286&amp;lat=-135.65625&amp;lng=59.197738&amp;zoom=8">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a></li> 
 <li>Capital Outskirts, at the end of the corridor past the elevator, on your left side. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=2855&amp;lat=-97.33&amp;lng=120.58&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=2855&amp;lat=-97.33&amp;lng=120.58&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</li> 
 <li>One&nbsp;is held by a corpse at <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Stormveil Castle" href="/Stormveil+Castle" target="">Stormveil Castle</a>, reached by descending through the stairs beside <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sites of grace" href="/Sites+of+grace">Stormveil Front Gates Site of Grace</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Video Location" href="https://youtu.be/7zS9MfxqlCs?t=2808">Video Location</a></li> 
 <li>One found under a wooden walkway in the eastern section of <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Castle Sol" href="/Castle+Sol" target="">Castle Sol</a>. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive map?id=3761&amp;lat=-59.867188&amp;lng=157.899361&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+map?id=3761&amp;lat=-59.867188&amp;lng=157.899361&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a></li> 
 <li>Found on the fortified manor, at <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Leyndell Royal Capital" href="/Leyndell+Royal+Capital" target="">Leyndell Royal Capital</a>. Inside the room with the fire. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive Map?id=3950&amp;lat=-104.44&amp;lng=112.22&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA" href="/Interactive+Map?id=3950&amp;lat=-104.44&amp;lng=112.22&amp;zoom=8&amp;code=mapA">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a></li> 
